  <context>
    <background>
      Pre-R7, the Action carried dispatch identity via `sprk_actiontypeid` lookup → `sprk_executoractiontype` INT.
      Post-R7, the node carries dispatch via `sprk_executortype`. The Action is now strictly a prompt-template carrier
      (SystemPrompt + OutputSchema + Temperature). This task simplifies the read path. Wave 4 drops the now-unused
      Dataverse fields.
    </background>
    <dependencies>
